---
title: SuperQuick Middle Eastern-Spiced Beef Bowls with Tahini-Dressed Salad and Spicy Drizzle
description: Pillowy couscous is the base of this recipe that's loaded with flavour and whipped up in a tight 15 minutes. Still short on time? Skip toasting the flatbreads and opt for fresh and fluffy instead!

